# Redirect all non-www to www
https://elderella.com/* https://www.elderella.com/:splat 301!
http://elderella.com/* https://www.elderella.com/:splat 301!
http://www.elderella.com/* https://www.elderella.com/:splat 301!

# Handle index.html to root URL
https://www.elderella.com/index.html https://www.elderella.com/ 301!

# Redirect trust to security (handle path-level redirect)
/trust /security 301!
